ĒíŔ@c260671e366af00ca11fc581de92e9384156052e3b8e36eb673f231ccc961162ŕ	Title: This Week in Nushell #254
Path: Nushell
Content:
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13306] fixed the variable completion sort order
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13242] forced completers to sort in fetch()
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13305] preserved attributes on external ByteStreams
lavafroth 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13301] fixed exotic types to return float on division and self on modulo
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13299] replaced 
``unfold``
 with 
``from_fn``
 for the generate command
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13300] changed duration mod duration to duration instead of float
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13290] created a better error message when saving fails
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13285] updated uutils crate versions
cablehead 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13297] removed the deprecated 
``register``
 command
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13296] ensured errors in examples don't show results
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13293] limited drilling down inside 
``explore``
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13268] made Span ID Refactor (Step 2): Make Call SpanId-friendly
 and then 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13292] reverted that change while we fix up some bugs
hqsz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13289] supported default offset with the dateformat option
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13286] checked if the cache is empty before enabling GC and added more logging
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13284] added the ability to set content-type metadata with 
``metadata set``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13254] allowed using pipeline data for HTTP post|put|patch|delete commands
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13277] fixed clippy lint
alex-tdrn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13274] skipped decoration lines for 
``detect columns --guess``
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13239] removed the deprecated 
``--numbered``
 flag from 
``for``
